at\nthe result for the emerging tau flux is in agreement with the result obtained\nusing analytic approach. Our results are relevant to several experiments that\nare looking for skimming astrophysical taus, such as the Pierre Auger\nObservatory, HAWC and Ashra. We evaluate the aperture for the Auger and discuss\nbriefly application to the the other two experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Mar 2017 20:27:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Jul 2017 16:19:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-16"}
