. Our methodology is\nimplemented in the R package MultiVarSel which is available from the CRAN\n(Comprehensive R Archive Network).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Mar 2017 22:29:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-04"}
