ould have or did come close to Canopus) drawn from various\nhistorical records is presented and discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 1 Apr 2017 14:08:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Jun 2018 13:03:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-04"}
